data.description: AMCEEBEE Group was founded in the year 1984 by Mr. Moolchand Bothra. The group started with Carpet Export business. In the year 1996 we ventured in to Realty business by starting the construction of a 1,00,000 sqft building in Varanasi.  The project was completed in 24 months and is one of the prominent properties of Varanasi.In the year 1998 his son Mr. Yash Bothra joined the business. He is the man behind the idea of venturing into Retail business. A robust future ahead….. A multi faceted corporate, with whole-hearted approach, dedication and acumen, these reflected in its being progressive and attributing to value addition. The group is managed by a well-knit team of professionals with proven expertise in their respective fields. We plan to open more than 100 Stores up to March 2012 in North India.
